            <lg xml:id="TK145">
<l>eḷiteṉa villiṟappā ṉeytumeñ ñāṉṟum</l>
<l>viḷiyātu niṟkum paḻi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who thinks it's no big deal to trespass in another's "house," obtains forever</l>
<l>an imperishable lasting shame.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
